    <Summary>/proc file system utilities</Summary>
    <Description>This project provides command line and full screen utilities for browsing procfs, a "pseudo" file system dynamically generated by the kernel to provide information about the status of entries in its process table (such as whether the process is running, stopped, or a "zombie").</Description>
